author: The Conversation
title: What the 2009 swine flu pandemic can tell us about the future of COVID-19
description: The first documented case of COVID-19 is thought to have appeared on December 1 2019 in Wuhan, China. Four months later, the world is in the middle of a pandemic with little idea of what comes next. Yet this is not the first pandemic to occur in recent years.…
